Money Back Guarantee

Every new device includes a 60-day money-back guarantee and a one (1) year warranty covering any manufacturer related problems resulting from everyday use of the product. An extended 2-year warranty is available for purchase (must be purchased before original 1-year warranty has expired) by contacting a representative at (888) 360-9171. NuFACE device attachments can be returned within 60-days of purchase and NuFACE Primers & Skin Care can be returned within 30-days. Refreshed NuFACE devices and attachments are FINAL SALE and cannot be returned unless received damaged. All Gift Cards are FINAL SALE and cannot be returned.
